text: George II, Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont (; 20 September 178915 May 1845) was Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont from 1813 to 1845. He was the son of George I, Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont and Princess Augusta of Schwarzburg- Sondershausen. Category:1789 births Category:1845 deaths Category:Princes of Waldeck and Pyrmont
